yle="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://en.internationalism.org/wr/313/may-68">"May 68: the student movement in France and the world"</a>. <i>Internationalism</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2015-12-19</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALeft+communism&amp;rft.atitle=May+68%3A+the+student+movement+in+France+and+the+world&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Internationalism&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fen.internationalism.org%2Fwr%2F313%2Fmay-68&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web">Lassou (May 2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://en.internationalism.org/print/book/export/html/4991">"Contribution to a history of the workers\xe2\x80\x99 movement in Africa (v): May 1968 in Senegal"</a>. <i>Internationalism</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2015-12-19</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALeft+communism&amp;rft.atitle=Contribution+to+a+history+of+the+workers%E2%80%99+movement+in+Africa+%28v%29%3A+May+1968+in+Senegal&amp;rft.au=Lassou&amp;rft.date=2012-05&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Internationalism&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fen.internationalism.org%2Fprint%2Fbook%2Fexport%2Fhtml%2F4991&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11">^</a><